data.title: United States Coast and Geodetic Survey : sketch showing the progress of the survey in section No. X (lower sheet) ; from San Diego to Pt. Sal ; from 1850 to 1883
data.meta_description: Map illustrates the progress of the coastal survey from San Diego to Pt. Sal by using occupied and unoccupied stations to triangulate positions along the coast from 1850 to 1883.
